<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4425549>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–6. Bezzia pulverea. Male, 1–3, Female, 4–6. 1 Apical mid-tibial spines. 2 Genitalia at focal level of aedeagus, gonocoxites and gonostyli. 3 Genitalia at focal level of sternite 9 and parameres. 4 Thorax and legs. 5 Wing. 6 Abdomen, ventral view of spermathecae." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4425549/files/figure.png" .

